{"id": 1728, "genre": 1000, "title": "你是哪一种播客用户？", "description": "各类 podcast、音频节目、主播电台，你都怎么听？（题图来自：ccoli）", "record_count": 4668, "comment_count": 34, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170606144209c5xKX6byiAF0Bklh.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-08T17:00:15Z", "questions": [{"id": 2413, "title": "你是哪一种播客用户？", "content": "你是哪一种播客用户？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 210129, "content": "密集信息接收型，无法接受 1.3 倍速还没啥有用信息的主播聊天", "image": "img/option/option/20170606145806LdipXQ4hgDsrxHmt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 210133, "content": "新鲜事型，听一堆人聊天扯淡没问题，只要能听到点以前不知道的东西", "image": "img/option/option/20170606151003qD0uPRzIG1aLfd6Z.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 210141, "content": "外语学习型，只听国外播客", "image": "img/option/option/201706061526426oBIhfbpYwlELQy3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 210143, "content": "随意型，只想耳机里有点东西随便播播", "image": "img/option/option/20170606163202cTx0KLgwpNaIn2rG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 210137, "content": "RSS型，有一系列喜欢的节目，不会错过它们的更新", "image": "img/option/option/20170606151819mdXUIWNMV7e1x98F.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 210147, "content": "忠粉型，会在不同的平台关注主播甚至参加线下活动", "image": "img/option/option/20170606163144axkdXfFlJ8TDV5Az.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 210158, "content": "助眠型，耳边一定要有点声音才睡得着", "image": "img/option/option/2017060714435791cJkXlpGqtSLzyC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 210157, "content": "通勤型，上下班在车上、地铁上听", "image": "img/option/option/20170607154653lkFsIBPCuZJmYwXr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 210148, "content": "基本没听过", "image": "img/option/option/201706061559414eiDvwIf3YRPXgdV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}